Buffer
C-x C-b : List buffers
C-x b 	: Switch to named buffer
C-x k 	: Close the current buffer

Cursor
C-f : Move the cursor 1 character forward
C-b : Move the cursor 1 character back
C-n : Move the cursor 1 line down
C-p : Move the cursor 1 line up
M-f : Move the cursor 1 word forward
M-b : Move the cursor 1 word backward
C-a : Move the cursor to a line beginning
C-e : Move the cursor to a line ending
M-a : Move the cursor to a paragraph beginning
M-e : Move the cursor to a paragraph ending
C-v : Move the cursor one page down
M-v : Move the cursor one page up
M-< : Move the cursor to a file beginning
M-> : Move the cursor to a file ending
C-| : Recenter the screen around the current line

Files
C-x C-f : Open a file
C-x C-s : Save a file
C-x C-w : Save a file as
C-x s	: Save a file (unsaved)

Frames
C-x 5 0 : Close current frame
C-x 5 1 : Close frame other all
C-x 5 2 : Create a new frame
C-x C-c : Exit emacs

Windows
C-x 0 : Close window current
C-x 1 : Close window other all
C-x 2 : Split window vertically
C-x 3 : Split window horizontally
C-x o : Toggle to other window